%% Diagram: Contract And Release Flow
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
  participant Domain as Domain team
  participant Contract as Contract artifact
  participant Registry as Registry
  participant Consumer as Consumer team
  participant Release as Release pipeline

  Domain->>Contract: 1. Evolve API, event, or package surface
  Domain->>Release: 2. Propose breaking change (RFC or ADR)
  Release->>Contract: 3. Apply semver bump policy
  Contract->>Registry: 4. Publish client, schema, or tarball
  Registry-->>Consumer: 5. Resolve compatible range with lockfile
  Consumer->>Consumer: 6. Integrate via adapter at boundary
  Note over Consumer,Contract: Deprecation window or release train for incompatible bumps
